{"tid":347881,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[流感] 5月5日起, 死咗307件","createTime":"2017-08-05T08:15:49.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-05T12:36:42.000Z","uid":79410,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"f842a522b033aa6b48dc603df2f632e573c7611b","tid":347881,"uid":79410,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-05T08:15:49.000Z","msg":"嚴重流感個案監測<br />\n(註：現時報告的是臨時數據，可能會因資料的更新而作出修訂)<br />\n<br />\n自 2017 年 5 月 5 日加強監測嚴重流感個案起，中心共錄得 450 宗嚴重個案，當中包括307 宗死亡個案(截至 8 月 2 日)(圖九)。這些個案包括： <br />\n<br />\n431 宗成人個案(年齡為十八歲或以上)，當中包括 304 宗死亡個案。這些個案中，有385 人感染甲型（H3N2）流感；21 人感染甲型(H1N1)pdm09 流感；13 人感染乙型流感；12 人感染甲型流感(有待分型)。已知 160 人(37.1%)曾接受 2016/17 年的流感疫苗注射。304 宗死亡個案中，已知 137 人(45.1%)曾接受流感疫苗注射。2017 年初的冬季流感季期間則有 66 宗成人嚴重個案(包括 41 宗死亡個案)。<br />\n<br />\n19 宗兒童流感相關之嚴重併發症/死亡個案，當中包括 3 宗死亡個案。17 宗個案(89.5%)沒有接受 2016/17 年的流感疫苗注射。2017 年至今共有 27 宗兒童嚴重個案(包括 4宗死亡個案)。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.chp.gov.hk/files/pdf/fluexpress_web_week30_3_8_2017_chi.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.chp.gov.hk%2Ffiles%2Fpdf%2Ffluexpress_web_week30_3_8_2017_chi.pdf&d=RteHjx9wNTTgmW3pMpHAc%2F1gJfeR7%2BEkjjir5NquRfg%3D&h=6899d23e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.chp.gov.hk/files/pdf/fluexpress_web_week30_3_8_2017_chi.pdf</a>"},{"pid":"5ba6ddedbeafd8757fb89e9d6085ce70e29d0065","tid":347881,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-05T08:34:37.000Z","msg":"港豬:經濟重要D,體諒政府隱瞞消息啦"},{"pid":"e744ff8937e66324dec7c25ddfc6e552c663ffbc","tid":347881,"uid":14716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-05T08:42:26.000Z","msg":"屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6cf9f8d8254935c424b2d0ea734e4187cc9ca585","tid":347881,"uid":51469,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-05T08:51:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>港豬:經濟重要D,體諒政府隱瞞消息啦</blockquote><br />\n你睇下份文件邊度黎既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f60d5556f5405012e07c153e7ea2b8e4fa8a5cd","tid":347881,"uid":15711,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-05T09:24:56.000Z","msg":"連登仔自己都無人回，但就不斷笑其他人係港豬？"},{"pid":"910faa380999bbae8ac50f408d546c0e930312cf","tid":347881,"uid":23023,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-05T09:30:11.000Z","msg":"電視永遠唔會報呢單新聞<br />\n驚死影響香港經濟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"996999bf0d7a5dc570787b4c2727ac7009c9bd5a","tid":347881,"uid":79410,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-05T09:50:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>港豬:經濟重要D,體諒政府隱瞞消息啦</blockquote><br />\n你睇下份文件邊度黎既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有文件, 但係唔喺電台, 電視講出嚟, 有乜用. <br />\n即係收收埋埋D 咨詢, 唔公佈, 根住就話咨詢完."},{"pid":"faeecffb8ace3b91ad78a90ae45d9d007372f201","tid":347881,"uid":79410,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-05T09:53:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>電視永遠唔會報呢單新聞<br />\n驚死影響香港經濟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n正仆街嚟"},{"pid":"3d20c79ea97314630e47001a159e12a0ef6aaa3a","tid":347881,"uid":53026,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-05T11:42:45.000Z","msg":"濕濕碎，日日百五人口新力軍"},{"pid":"5db8770a5d9fad6ffb6a0544e88f82eb702fec35","tid":347881,"uid":51469,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-05T12:31:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>港豬:經濟重要D,體諒政府隱瞞消息啦</blockquote><br />\n你睇下份文件邊度黎既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有文件, 但係唔喺電台, 電視講出嚟, 有乜用. <br />\n即係收收埋埋D 咨詢, 唔公佈, 根住就話咨詢完.</blockquote><br />\n<a href=\"https://topick.hket.com/article/1871880/%E4%BB%8A%E5%A4%8F%E6%B5%81%E6%84%9F%E6%9A%AB%E5%A5%AA299%E5